Get Packages by biocViews

Source: R/example.R
get_packages_by_view.Rd

Get Packages by biocViews

get_packages_by_view(view)

Arguments

view

One biocView term.

Value

Character vector of package names.

Examples

get_packages_by_view("Sequencing")
